!!! Key Points

* Set `handlePosition="overlay"` to enable overlay mode
* The parent element must have `position: relative`
* Style the resizer handle with `position: absolute` and position it using `top`, `right`, `bottom`, `left`
* Use semi-transparent backgrounds for better visual feedback
* Make handles at least 8-12px wide/tall for easy grabbing

!!! Minimal Code Example

```html
<style>
.my-resizer-handle {
  position: absolute;
  right: 0;
  top: 0;
  bottom: 0;
  width: 10px;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
  cursor: ew-resize;
}
</style>

<div style.position="relative" style.width={{!!width}} style.height="200px" style.background="#f0f0f0">
  Content here
  <$resizer 
    tiddler=<<currentTiddler>>
    field="width"
    handlePosition="overlay"
    class="my-resizer-handle"
  />
</div>
```